Based on the gathered evidence, it appears that integration with legacy systems poses a significant overhead for companies like Acme FinTech. FinTechCo, a similar company, was able to cut their onboarding time from 6 weeks to 2 weeks by implementing robust APIs and SDKs, leading to a typical 3-5x ROI within the first year.

Let's draft an email to Alex Rivera, VP of Engineering at Acme FinTech, highlighting these benefits and proposing a discovery call to discuss how our APIs and SDKs can help streamline their integration process.

Subject: Proposal: Streamline Integration Process with Our APIs & SDKs
Body: Hi Alex, I understand that you're facing integration challenges with legacy systems at Acme FinTech. We've helped companies like FinTechCo reduce their integration time by ~60% and achieve a typical 3-5x ROI within the first year. Could we schedule a 20-minute discovery call to discuss how our APIs and SDKs can help streamline your integration process?
